00:13:35,680 --> 00:13:37,880
Payday loan companies
present themselves as a way

261
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:39,880
for you to get back
onto your feet.

262
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:41,880
They don't want you
to get trapped in debt.

263
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:44,680
In fact, they'll help you
if you fall behind.

264
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:47,640
Remember the friendly
