265
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:49,680
What happens if you can't
pay back your loan?

266
00:13:49,880 --> 00:13:52,080
Sometimes people have
a hard time paying us back,

267
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:54,920
and we'll be there to work
with you if that should happen.

268
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:58,600
Yeah, no shit you'll
