327
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:41,800
and that brings us to why
the payday loan industry

328
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,800
is seemingly unstoppable.

329
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:46,800
They are incredibly good
at avoiding regulation.

330
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:48,800
Just look at
one example in Texas.

331
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:53,200
They actually tried to rein in the payday loan industry there
a few years ago,

332
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:57,320
