a store right there.

341
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:26,800
That man is Texas State
Representative Gary Elkins,

342
00:17:27,000 --> 00:17:29,000
and his proud defense
of the little guy

343
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:31,800
is about to get
a little muddier.

