00:19:09,080 --> 00:19:11,880
is also, at the same time,
a vice president

377
00:19:12,080 --> 00:19:14,880
of one of the biggest payday
loan companies in the country.

378
00:19:15,080 --> 00:19:17,880
I call dingo.
I call dingo on that man.

379
00:19:18,080 --> 00:19:21,280
I call dingo on him!
I call dingo!

380
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:23,880
Dingo, dingo, dingo!

381
00:19:24,080 --> 00:19:26,880
So let's just quickly
break all of that down.

382
00:19:27,080 --> 00:19:30,880
If you are hoping to protect Texans from the
payday loan industry,

383
00:19:31,080 --> 00:19:34,280
you would need to approach a commission overseen
by the vice president

384
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:37,880
of a payday loan company
